  "background": "A large bank wants to estimate the average amount of money owed by its delinquent debtors, denoted as μ. The bank randomly samples n=100 delinquent accounts and finds that the sample mean amount owed is $230. It is known that the standard deviation of the amount owed for all delinquent accounts is $90. The task is to calculate a confidence interval for the target parameter μ using the interval estimator formula.",
  "task": [
